---

<section id="services" class="py-32">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mb-20" data-animate>
      <p class="text-accent text-sm font-medium mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider">Our philosophy</p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-display mb-6 tracking-tight">
        Emotion is the heart<br/>of every <span class="text-accent">decision</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Whether it's a product or a service, people choose with their hearts, not just their heads. We create the digital world your brand lives in.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16" data-animate>
      <div>
        <div class="text-xs font-mono text-text-muted mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">The typical agency</div>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Hands you a template, calls it "custom"
          </li>
          <li class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Disappears after launch, no support
          </li>
          <li class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Bills by the hour, scope creeps forever
          </li>
          <li class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Builds what looks good, not what converts
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="text-xs font-mono text-accent mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">How we work</div>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="text-text leading-relaxed">
            We research your market before writing code
          </li>
          <li class="text-text leading-relaxed">
            Fixed-price projects, no surprise invoices
          </li>
          <li class="text-text leading-relaxed">
            We're still here after launch — optimizing, not vanishing
          </li>
          <li class="text-text leading-relaxed">
            Every decision backed by data, not guesswork
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
